Advertisement call. —The advertisement call was recorded on Chittagong University campus at an air temperature of 24 ºC. The call consists of a very fast trill series of three note types : a group of similar pulsed trains ( type 1 ) interspersed by short single notes (both type 2 and 3 , or just type 3 notes) with 775 ms (N= 1 ) of duration (
Fig. 4
).
